{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f8d8adee89","title":"戚本禹谈北京市的干部","origin":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a991c84a9e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"f8d8adee89"}],"tags":[{"id":"57434e107b","name":"戚本禹","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3a8bef265e","type":"title","text":"戚本禹谈北京市的干部","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f8d8adee89"},{"id":"66c4034b18","type":"authors","text":"戚本禹","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f8d8adee89"},{"id":"b53c4fb2cd","type":"subtitle","text":"(1967年3月初)","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f8d8adee89"},{"id":"352b52d26c","type":"paragraph","text":"北京市的老干部有的是好的，比较好的；有的是坏的，如雍文涛。市委的吴德、刘建勋、丁国钰、高扬文、李清泉是比较好的。今天来的几个同志是愿意跟毛主席走的，可以工作的。他们有经验，打过仗，搞过罢工，我们没有搞过，搞过学生运动，这还不够。今后揪他们要经过谢副总理批准，这是中央委托他做的。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f8d8adee89"}],"page":{"id":"ac61c7ad02","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f8d8adee89","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}